Summary: Gray saucer appeared from behind a mountain, headed level towards east.
divs: Sighting DetailsWhile on vacation in Ireland I took this photo overlooking Lough Leane in County Kerry, just east of the popular "Ladies View" area. I was aiming for my shot of the landscape, when I saw the object come into view. I watched it cross the sky until it went out-of-sight behind the hills on the left. We had seen a helicopter just a few moments before this, headed in the opposite direction, but at a greater altitude. In the attached picture, you'll see the object just left of center, above the hill. A second picture attached is my attempt at creating a close-up view from the original picture. Thanks, Mike
